src:
Témoignages décès Papo Mané / Ignace Ndèye, son ami intime raconte leur dernier instant et leur voyage Dakar-Ziguinchor.
03 Nov 2019 by Dakaractu




Ami intime de feu Mamadou Papo Mané, le correspondant de SudFm à Ziguinchor, Ignace Ndèye lors des témoignages dans la maison mortuaire sis au quartier Colobane, est revenu sur leur dernier voyage Dakar-Ziguinchor.
text:
Testimony Death Papo Mané / Ignace Ndèye, his intimate friend tells their last moment and their trip Dakar-Ziguinchor.
03 Nov 2019 by Dakaractu




Intimate friend of the late Mamadou Papo Mané, the correspondent of SudFm in Ziguinchor, Ignace Ndèye during the testimonies in the mortuary house in Colobane district, returned on their last Dakar-Ziguinchor trip.
